      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CERULEAN POPPY (2) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (17.27) at this track. Solid record here winning two races. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Sure to be about the mark. MAD HOWLER (4) finished sixth last time (17.61) at this track after winning at his previous three outings. Has a good record here at this journey. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Expected to feature in the finish. MY BOY BEAST (8) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 16.86 beating Round Up. Can make it back-to-back wins. CRACKER DUST (1) hit the frame here last start and can sneak into the finish again.",
